    "# ReAct Implementation: Reasoning + Acting for Complex Problem Solving\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook demonstrates the implementation and usage of ReAct (Reasoning + Acting) pattern in OpenDistillery for complex business problem solving.\n",
    "\n",
    "## What is ReAct?\n",
    "ReAct combines reasoning and acting in language models by having them:\n",
    "1. **Think** - Generate reasoning traces\n",
    "2. **Act** - Take actions based on reasoning\n",
    "3. **Observe** - Process action results\n",
    "4. **Repeat** - Continue until solution is found\n",
    "\n",
    "## Business Applications:\n",
    "- Strategic planning and analysis\n",
    "- Multi-step problem solving\n",
    "- Research and investigation\n",
    "- Complex decision making"
   ]
  },
